# Research protocol

Read and follow [`RESEARCH_PROTOCOL.md`](../../RESEARCH_PROTOCOL.md).

Hard rules for agents:

- Never write the PREDICT line — human only (`solving/experiments/predictions.md`).
- When asked what to run next: return §2 OPTIONS format (max 3) and stop.
- One variable per card.
- Do not implement an option the human did not pick.
- Mechanism stories go in `HYPOTHESES.md` until a metrics/figure citation exists.
- Experiment dirs need `NOTE.md` before they count ([`solving/experiments/LAYOUT.md`](../../solving/experiments/LAYOUT.md)).
